              li Custom themes with integrated IDX built in, all under your brand
              li Create a new, recurring revenue stream to scale your business
              li Serve clients in US and Canada
              li Receive gold standard support, training and other partner perks
              li Receive full support from IDX Boost team
            strong Ready to become an IDX Boost partner? Let’s Chat!
        
        .idx-box-lateral-b
